com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.common.listing

Class AbstractListResponse<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.common.listing.AbstractListResponse<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - element type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IdListResponse, ListResponse

    @Preamble(description="Generic paginated response corresponding to one page.")
public abstract class AbstractListResponse<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
    Most listing operations are paginated and respond with truncated results. This object comprises the information related to one page.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
